>\n啲人成日話撞鬼，究竟見到嘅係中陰身定係餓鬼？又點解會出現？<br />\n佛家認為死亡時就會因業力牽引而投生六道，行善多就可以投生上三道，反之則落下三道。<br />\n據記載，人死後會死七次，七日一生死，總共四十九日都要投胎<br />\n主要根據《業論》、《瑜伽師地論》等作為藍本，來一場有關生與死的分享<br />\n附上西藏唐卡的六道輪迴圖：<br />\n<a href=\"https://gss0.baidu.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy/zhidao/pic/item/4bed2e738bd4b31cf02939a084d6277f9e2ff890.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss0.baidu.com%2F7Po3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy%2Fzhidao%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F4bed2e738bd4b31cf02939a084d6277f9e2ff890.jpg&d=fW%2FbMTssWaiVGVkll%2FHuLf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=42aa1373\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gss0.baidu.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy/zhidao/pic/item/4bed2e738bd4b31cf02939a084d6277f9e2ff890.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"b261b7364d98127d54931566aa52acd16787f374","tid":449251,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T10:43:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43199370892e0b4967e03394d813e967eb0e748f","tid":449251,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea501bd3739919cb4da217ad1f1db82bc7268a3b","tid":449251,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:48:55.000Z","msg":"請問係有人去演講定點"},{"pid":"79b4210da85e232dd872672c6b79f0fe44cbd199","tid":449251,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:49:39.000Z","msg":"四十九日要投胎真係佛說？"},{"pid":"c65cf00ab64a055f91cccd099bde5da4ec7ac645","tid":449251,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:58:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問係有人去演講定點</blockquote><br />\n分享會形式，有主講人"},{"pid":"8d8ff33899a1a184d9e4063c4c5b589dc465c10c","tid":449251,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:01:32.000Z","msg":"Tg:<a href=\"https://t.me/Jeffrey1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FJeffrey1&d=fW%2FbMTssWaiVGVkll%2FHuLf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=bbd1a045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Jeffrey1</a>"},{"pid":"70e1f719e342da76704ce26733e717d1c38bc806","tid":449251,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb2c38023a6a29cea55cd471556344cb9447bf0","tid":449251,"uid":50408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84349c1da63cedded6e62b9a307c279732c2cc98","tid":449251,"uid":93091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:01:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>四十九日要投胎真係佛說？</blockquote><br />\n又此中有。若未得生緣極七日住。有得生緣即不決定。若極七日未得生緣死而復<br />\n生。極七日住。如是展轉未得生緣。乃至七七日住。自此已後決得生緣。<br />\n《瑜伽師地論》彌勒菩薩說  三藏法師玄奘奉　詔譯<br />\n<br />\n是次將會以唯識瑜伽行派的為本，加上彌勒菩薩的《瑜伽師地論》及世親菩薩的《成業論》，簡單分享一下業力和輪迴的佛學思想，合十"},{"pid":"f6bbf000d73c4d351f87f5cdff489efcd3cddf93","tid":449251,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294fecb683b768acc50c53549344c49fc8cbf6c2","tid":449251,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T15:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efcb28e7d84140e402ec79f0ed3248fd38cd8658","tid":449251,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T01:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff2a4381783d383d9a4643e3c1476a7db7e31d3","tid":449251,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:03:24.000Z","msg":"<img s